<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَأَمَّا جُمْهُورُ الْمَالِكِيَّةِ فَيَقُولُونَ:</span> إِنَّ الْجِعْرَانَةَ وَالتَّنْعِيمَ مُتَسَاوِيَانِ، وَلاَ أَفْضَلِيَّةَ لِوَاحِدٍ مِنْهُمَا عَلَى الآْخَرِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَتَفْصِيل ذَلِكَ فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c1">" إِحْرَامٌ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>جُعْلٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> جِعَالَةٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
